NAME
    AnyEvent::IRC::Server - An event based IRC protocol server API

SYNOPSIS
      use AnyEvent::IRC::Server;

DESCRIPTION
    AnyEvent::IRC::Server is

ROADMAP
        - useful for XIRCD
        -- authentication

        - useful for public irc server
        -- anti flooder
        -- limit nick length
        -- detect nick colision
        -- support /kick
        -- mode support
        -- who support

